1) Go to your terminal and type crontab -l
This will list all the cron jobs scheduled
2) Type crontab -e
This will open a default vi editor
3) type I for insert mode and schedule the cron job as following
15 0 * * * /usr/bin/python3 egenV1.py >> output

We have scheduled the job to take place at 12:15 AM everyday everymonth everyyear as in the description of the URL it was mentioned that database updates at 12:00 AM everyday, so we keep a buffer of 15 mins

we can check scheduled job by crontab -l
